    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295610/extras/f78d4dbe6f83a8a155bfc249420dc2ef.webp?t=1744881008\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295610/extras/f26682b091453b466c31cae1990b6abd.poster.avif?t=1744881008\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295610/extras/f26682b091453b466c31cae1990b6abd.webm?t=1744881008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295610/extras/f26682b091453b466c31cae1990b6abd.mp4?t=1744881008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295610/extras/c755ba84010a4f4a24d9b27bdc1b7095.webp?t=1744881008\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><br><i>&quot;王子啊，请知晓，当亚特兰蒂斯统治大洋的那些年代，罪恶和傲慢释放了凶恶的恶魔。当一切似乎已经失落时，四位英雄来到这里，关闭了阿巴索尔的大门。&quot;</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295610/extras/3ad45b99d9bc8a7fd0751b89f62acc30.poster.avif?t=1744881008\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295610/extras/3ad45b99d9bc8a7fd0751b89f62acc30.webm?t=1744881008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295610/extras/3ad45b99d9bc8a7fd0751b89f62acc30.mp4?t=1744881008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>亚特兰蒂斯文明激怒了众神。他们派遣了一群怪物来惩罚亚特兰蒂斯，摧毁大陆。玩家必须合作和竞争，以拯救亚特兰蒂斯，通过一系列越来越困难的挑战。在他们的进程中，我们的英雄将与凶恶的恶魔和原始的神祇作战，与生者和死者作战，与飞禽走兽和爬行恐怖作战。他们将躲避危险和陷阱，陷入阴森的深渊。但他们也会互相竞争，争夺战利品和掠夺财宝，并将其奉献给神灵以获得祝福。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295610/extras/aa96d799fd52f6b2636bb76bc443c3ac.poster.avif?t=1744881008\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295610/extras/aa96d799fd52f6b2636bb76bc443c3ac.webm?t=1744881008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295610/extras/aa96d799fd52f6b2636bb76bc443c3ac.mp4?t=1744881008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295610/extras/c755ba84010a4f4a24d9b27bdc1b7095.webp?t=1744881008\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>受动作Rogue-lite影响的2D平台游戏，本地模式下最多可支持4名玩家。<br></li><li>通过超过50个难度递增的关卡和令人难以置信的最终Boss，与一群怪物作战。<br></li><li>享受精心制作的像素艺术和超过40首史诗音乐曲目。<br></li><li>穿越整个亚特兰蒂斯大陆，深入探索基于柏拉图著作和阿坦纳修斯地图的故事背景。<br></li><li>重温80年代和90年代的街机游戏，具有复古16位游戏的特点，并受metroidvania和beat 'em up类型的影响。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295610/extras/ee91d269729bb420fce35b347a30994c.poster.avif?t=1744881008\" width=600 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295610/extras/ee91d269729bb420fce35b347a30994c.webm?t=1744881008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295610/extras/ee91d269729bb420fce35b347a30994c.mp4?t=1744881008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
